author: Sheena McGinley
title: Watch: Child swears blind he didn't eat a cupcake
text:
Young Jack here claims he's not had a cupcake recently. He repeatedly says 'No', 'no cupcake' and even - at one point - he suggest he was elsewhere ('at home' - despite being at the Giants game) at the time of the alleged cupcake consumption.
Jack, you've a bright future as a politician ahead of you. Almost as bright as that invisible cupcake icing.
